{"tid":38470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"游蕙禎：已有新法律觀點 將上訴至終院","createTime":"2016-12-14T02:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T04:58:48.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c538e51711bcaf82a3f6f6e88e2928bcf8030867","tid":38470,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:54:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161214/large/1481683326_642f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161214%2Flarge%2F1481683326_642f.jpg&h=992c29d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青年新政梁頌恆及游蕙禎早前就被撤銷議員資格提上訴，但遭上訴庭駁回。兩人今早於高等法院門外見記者，游蕙禎指與律師團隊已找到新的法律觀點，故將於上訴限期前以新的方向向終院提上訴，並指須在1月前交出160萬按金以完成上訴程序，他們會繼續眾籌，透露至今已籌得44萬元，並已用作支付律師費。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭早前於判詞中指，按人大釋法解釋的《基本法》104條及香港法例，兩人在法律上已自動喪失議員資格並離任，法律上不可能容許兩人重新宣誓。"},{"pid":"141a1d0755573fb02e05f2829ce093a3eef92ea8","tid":38470,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"12e553fe6caab185e4105b6e533dbe47914b460e","tid":38470,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"咪撚獻醜啦屌！柒唔夠咩"},{"pid":"bf983f2a6bfbeff8ee4090cabe80ba62f07027c2","tid":38470,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:56:28.000Z","msg":"( Show Blocked User - 溫哥華陳浩南 )"},{"pid":"486bbeb50b480d0983dea70196f59cab06589d73","tid":38470,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:56:36.000Z","msg":"咩新法律觀點？<br />\n唔好忘記基本法最終解釋權及修改權在人大！"},{"pid":"9c660780058b8133f3ee38ac64f48cc4ca410444","tid":38470,"uid":7942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T02:57:31.000Z","msg":"段歷史係想表達啲乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab158a60442216